      <title>MacOS环境配置</title>
      <link href="/2023/03/15/MacOS%E9%9A%90%E8%97%8F%E7%94%A8%E6%88%B7%E5%90%8D%E5%8F%8A%E8%AE%A1%E7%AE%97%E6%9C%BA%E5%90%8D/"/>
      <url>/2023/03/15/MacOS%E9%9A%90%E8%97%8F%E7%94%A8%E6%88%B7%E5%90%8D%E5%8F%8A%E8%AE%A1%E7%AE%97%E6%9C%BA%E5%90%8D/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="MacOS基础环境配置"><a href="#MacOS基础环境配置" class="headerlink" title="MacOS基础环境配置"></a>MacOS基础环境配置</h1><h2 id="终端配置"><a href="#终端配置" class="headerlink" title="终端配置"></a>终端配置</h2><h3 id="终端隐藏用户名及计算名"><a href="#终端隐藏用户名及计算名" class="headerlink" title="终端隐藏用户名及计算名"></a>终端隐藏用户名及计算名</h3><p>目前最新的MacOS，默认的终端使用的是zsh，打开终端，默认显示了用户名@计算机名 当前目录$，默认配置如下：</p><pre class="line-numbers language-zsh" data-language="zsh"><code class="language-zsh">export PS1="%n@%m %1~ %# "<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span></span></code></pre><p>通过在/Users/用户名/.zshrc增加以下语句，保存。</p><pre class="line-numbers language-zsh" data-language="zsh"><code class="language-zsh">export PS1="%%1~ %# "<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span></span></code></pre><p>如果没有/Users/用户名/.zshrc文件，需要新建。</p><pre class="line-numbers language-zsh" data-language="zsh"><code class="language-zsh">cd ~vi .zshrc<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre><p>执行source /Users/用户名/.zshrc使其生效。</p><pre class="line-numbers language-zsh" data-language="zsh"><code class="language-zsh">source /Users/用户名/.zshrc<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span></span></code></pre><h2 id="后端开发环境配置"><a href="#后端开发环境配置" class="headerlink" title="后端开发环境配置"></a>后端开发环境配置</h2><h2 id="前端开发环境配置"><a href="#前端开发环境配置" class="headerlink" title="前端开发环境配置"></a>前端开发环境配置</h2>]]></content>
      
      
